<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to {{saasName}}!</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: {{primaryColor}};
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: {{primaryColor}};
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 0.8em;
            color: #777;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Welcome to {{saasName}}!</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <p>Dear {{userName}},</p>
        <p>We're thrilled to welcome you to {{saasName}}! Thank you for choosing our platform to help you {{saasBenefit}}.</p>
        <p>Here are a few things you can do to get started:</p>
        <ul>
            {{#each gettingStartedSteps}}
                <li>{{this}}</li>
            {{/each}}
        </ul>
        <p>{{supportMessage}}</p>
        <a href="{{ctaLink}}" class="button">{{ctaText}}</a>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <p>Â© {{currentYear}} {{saasName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>{{footerMessage}}</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>